{
  "texts": [
    "For instance, it can provide localized climate-risk assessments for specific regions or cities far into the future, something that was traditionally challenging due to the broad-brush approach required for long-term forecasts.",
    "In essence, probabilistic AI breaks the conventional link between spatial and temporal scales in forecasting, enabling more precise and detailed long-term predictions.",
    "This advancement is crucial for effective risk assessment and planning in the context of climate change and weather variability.",
    "In summary, a multi-modal Early Warning FM holds promise for enhancing crisis response mechanisms.",
    "By processing and interpreting a diverse array of data types, these models can provide valuable insights and predictions in real time."
  ]
}